'''''Rough Justice''''' ({{lang-it|La belva}}) is a 1970 Italian [[Western (genre)|Western film]] directed by [[Mario Costa (director)|Mario Costa]] and starring [[Klaus Kinski]].<ref name="NY Times">{{cite web |url=http://movies.nytimes.com/movie/141338/La-Belva/overview |title=New York Times: Rough Justice |accessdate=2008-10-25|work=NY Times}}</ref>

